@superpaperdude:
[Spend 3 days downloading this. The installer first locked my computer up three times...then when it DID install, it got to the NVIDIA PhysX installer...which I already have on my system, and it says it can't open the installer. Incompatible with windows 7 ultimate x64 i guess. no way around it.]

W7 x64 here as well and it runs like a charm.  For reference, you can always just use 7zip to unpack the installer.  It isn't really an installer, after all, it's more of a smart unpacker.  The only thing that doesn't get done that way is redists, like PhysX, and if you already have it, you don't need to install it again.

